E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Alright, man. Let's drop the hammer on that shit. I'll be by soon.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~好啊，兄弟。到时候赛场上见。有空就来。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Their buns are perter than yours and they'd kill to hook a closeted, bald bigot like Bryce.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~他们的屁股可比你诱人多了，都排着队钓Bryce这种深柜的秃头政客呢。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~How's your fancy European friend working out?
~z~There's cops on wiretaps waiting to bust us, and there's monsters in the closet, and every chick in this town
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~条子成天窃听我们电话等着抓人，每个衣柜里都有怪兽，全自由城的妓女

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~These calls tell me you're full of shit. You wanna talk to me again, get me in bracelets.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~打电话就说明你没有证据。还想跟我说话，就先逮捕我吧。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~If it's a race you want, my brother.
~z~I hope so for your sake Johnny, you know. Ha ha. See you soon, baby.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~希望如你所说吧，Johnny。哈哈。再见了，宝贝。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~La La La La La La La, just be good to me.
~z~(SINGING) Living my life like it's golden... living my life like it's golden... living my life like it's golden.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~(唱歌) 度过我黄金般的人生... 度过我黄金般的人生。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~They coming, Johnny. They fucking coming right now, you know.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~他们来了，Johnny。现在他们他妈来了。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~You're about to see a close friend on the witness stand.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~你会在证言台上看见自己的密友。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~No, man, I'm coming. Chill the fuck out.
~z~You've still got it Bernie. You don't need this stupid car. You're the precision machine.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~你还是可以的，Bernie。你不需要这辆破车。你可是精密仪器。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Yeah, only problem was your friend the UC. He nearly blew my ass off.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~是啊，只不过你那买家朋友是个卧底。差点没把我阴死。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~See if you can catch me, lady.
~z~Okay, okay. Seems like maybe he's the only guy in this city not working for the state.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~挺好，挺好。他可能是城里唯一一个不替政府干活的人了。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I heard 'em alright, but we're cool. Girl does bring heat to a deal, Billy.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~我全听说了，但是没事。女人确实会让交易被盯上，Billy。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Maybe the lips as well as the forehead. Hmmm? If you want to keep Bryce, Bernie, it's gonna cost you.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~我看应该去打几针了。要么把额头跟嘴唇一起打了吧。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Liz Torres. Keep one eye open, Johnny. You heard the tales.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~Liz Torres。还是要当心啊，Johnny。你也听说了吧。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Nope. You want me, come and get me.
~z~Yeah, umm, good luck, Liz. Is Marta okay?
~z~(Shouting) Get out of the way, you stupid man!
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~(大喊) 好狗不挡道，傻逼玩意！

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Things might be easier for you if you give us some information on your motorcycle club.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~告诉我你们摩托帮的情报，你的日子会好过很多。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Oh! (SINGING) Living my life like it's Golden, sweetie!
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~哦！ (唱歌) 度过我黄金般的人生，宝贝！

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~The problem is we can't have a real discussion, and can't solve any real fuckin' problems,
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~如果你不来会所，不肯和弟兄们坐下聊聊，

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Shit, dude, you can really twist it.
~z~Open her up. Twist that fuckin' throttle.
~z~What a fantastic idea, James. I'll see you at yours.
~z~if you aren't gonna come to the house and sit down with your brothers.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~我们就谈不成事，更没法成什么事！

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I was on fucking rails back there. You didn't stand a chance.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~我刚才状态极佳，你不可能赢的。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~As it happens, others in your fraternity are not as loyal as you.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~实际上，不是所有弟兄都和你一样守口如瓶的。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~What do you mean "a PTA meeting," Bryce? That bitch squeezed out those monsters to put a death grip on you.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~「家长会」是什么意思，Bryce？那个婊子造出这种怪物是想害死你啊。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I'll believe it when I see it, you tight-ass prick. Adios.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~先让我见着再说，傻逼儿子。再见。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Boys still looking. Ah. Bernie you've got it.
~z~If you had anything on me, I'd have been arrested already, man.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~要是你真有证据，我早就进去了，老兄。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Don't get me started on the brats. Don't get me started! I'm having a hot flush here, people.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~别让我想到臭小孩。别让我想到它！这可是我的逆鳞，各位。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~The floor was mine. Oh, and did you see Luis?
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~吸引了所有人的目光。哦，你看见Luis了吗？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Fuck. I'll beat your slow ass next round, man.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~操，下次比赛看我不干烂你，老兄。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Tiralo. Tira el perico. Oh Shit. Flush that shit! Tira el perico!
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~扔掉。把可卡因扔掉。妈的。赶紧冲掉！冲掉可卡因！

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~An insect who chugs vodka sodas and sucks all the life out of my precious Bryce.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~是一个喝着伏特加苏打水、吸干我宝贝Bryce生命的虫子。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Shit, dude. I'll fucking get you next time.
~z~So many boys get off that bus everyday.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~要想留住Bryce可不容易。每天都会遇到那么多人。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I hope you ain't slow in your old age, Bill.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~希望你的年龄不会影响发挥，Bill。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Bring it, Bill. Let's do some dicing.
~z~I was dripping sweat and sex and buzzing on X and amyl.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~我浑身湿透，性欲超强，尽显摇头丸和Amyl的本色。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Yeah, yeah, ours is going through the roof. See you soon.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~对对，就我们做得红红火火。再见。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Fuck you, Fed. This conversation's over. If you got any evidence on me, get a warrant.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~操你妈，狗腿子。对话到此为止。你要是有我犯罪的证据，拿逮捕令来抓我。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Him and The Lost MC. Me and the brothers are tight.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~失落帮也一样。弟兄们和我绝不告密。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~You flogged that bitch, man. Good win.
~z~Hey, asshole. I'd never roll on a brother.
~z~Johnny, it's Jim, you wanna roll on some Deadbeats?
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~Johnny，我是Jim，你想去教训死妈天使吗？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Let's drop that hammer one more time.
~z~What you got in that block, man? You really blasted it.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~那段路是怎么回事，老兄？你也太猛了吧。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Whoa, hey, you like the taste of that exhaust?
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~喔，嘿，喜欢精疲力尽的滋味吗？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Let's see what you're made of. Come on.
~z~It was good to see you, Johnny.
~z~Bernie! Ahhhh! What is that on your face? Ewww. I think it's time for some shots.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~Bernie！啊！看了眼镜子我都要吐了。你脸上都是什么啊？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~A race? Too fucking right. I'm in, man. I'll be there as soon as I can.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~赛车？当然有兴趣。我来，兄弟。有空了就来。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~The X! I felt like some tribal rhythm had taken a hold of me.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~那摇头丸！感觉就像是被哪种部落摇摆附身了。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~You know, Johnny, you should have thought about being more forthcoming earlier in our relationship.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~真的，Johnny，你早就该和我们多聊点真心话了。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~You tried to offload some smack to a colleague of mine called Charlie. Costly mistake.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~你之前想把毒品卖给我的同事Charlie。交了不少学费。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I got work, Johnny. You should be grateful. While them other markets be dropping...
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~有新活，Johnny。快感谢我吧。现在其他地方可不景气...

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~I don't know what the fuck you're talking about.
~z~has got VD Shit, Johnny, you spook too easy. Get it sold.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~都有性病。妈的，Johnny，你也太怂了。把货卖了。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~You're a fast sonofabitch, man. Good win.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~你这贱逼有够快啊，老兄。厉害。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~If he ever plays for our team, I hope I'm the catcher, sweetie. I do!
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~要是他来我们队效力，我希望我是捕手，宝贝。真的。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Are you too good for that now, Johnny?
~z~Jonathan, man, I was thinking you and me could enter a race together. How about it?
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~Jonathan，兄弟，我在想要不要一起去赛车。你说呢？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Hercules was a dream, wasn't it? The music! The bodies!
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~大力神太梦幻了，不是吗？那音乐！那肉体！

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Johnny, it's Terry. Listen, bro, I heard there's a race going down and thought you might be interested?
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~Johnny，我是Terry。听着，兄弟，听说附近有地方赛车，你有兴趣吗？

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Every cop in this town wants that bitch's head on his wall.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~全城的警察都想要那个婊子的项上人头。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~Agent Jones - FIB. We'd like you to come in for a talk.
~z~Shit, for a bitch you ride good.
~z~Oh, we all good, baby. Ha, ha, ha. Bye bye.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~哦，我们都很好，宝贝。哈哈哈。拜拜。

E1MF3AU.original: ~z~(SINGING) I don't care what you do to me, just be good to me.
E1MF3AU.translated: ~z~(唱歌) 不在乎你怎么对我，对我好就行
